                <div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Pause Reason <span class="text-danger">*</span></label><textarea id="pauseTaskNotes" class="form-control" rows="2"></textarea></div>
                <div class="alert alert-warning py-2" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">
                    <h6 class="alert-heading fw-bold mb-1"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale me-1"></i> Capacity Impact</h6>
                    <p class="mb-0">The estimated hours for this task will be <strong>immediately removed</strong> from the user's workload scorecard and the global Org Capacity metrics.</p>
