<!-- Info: Org Capacity -->
<div class="modal fade" id="infoOrgCapacityModal" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content border-0">
            <div class="modal-header bg-light"><h5 class="modal-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Algorithm: Org Capacity</h5><button class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <p><strong>What it means:</strong> Represents the immediate workload across the entire organization, helping executives determine if teams can absorb new projects or if they are overextended.</p>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Calculations:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Available Hours:</strong> Total number of active team members × 40 hours sprint capacity.</li>
                    <li><strong>Committed Hours:</strong> Sum of <code>EstimatedHours</code> for all tasks that are NOT 'Done' and NOT 'Paused'.</li>
                    <li><strong>Utilization %:</strong> <code>(Committed Hours / Available Hours) × 100</code></li>
                </ul>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Status Thresholds:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-success">Free</span>: &lt; 50% utilization</li>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">Balanced</span>: 50% – 80% utilization</li>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-danger bg-opacity-75">At Risk</span>: 80% – 100% utilization</li>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-danger">Overloaded</span>: &gt; 100% utilization</li>
                </ul>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">New Project Recommendation:</h6>
                <p class="mb-0 text-muted">A "Yes" is given only if Utilization &lt; 70% AND there are exactly zero projects categorized as "At Risk" (projects having overdue tasks).</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Info: Portfolio Health Scores -->
<div class="modal fade" id="infoPortHealthModal" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content border-0">
            <div class="modal-header bg-light"><h5 class="modal-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle text-danger me-2"></i>Algorithm: Portfolio Health Score</h5><button class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <p><strong>What it means:</strong> A 0-100 composite score indicating the momentum, on-time delivery, and active engagement for each project.</p>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Scoring Weights:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Completion Rate (40 points):</strong> % of tasks marked as 'Done' vs Total Tasks.</li>
                    <li><strong>On-Time Rate (40 points):</strong> % of active tasks that are NOT overdue past their due date.</li>
                    <li><strong>Team Engagement (20 points):</strong> % of team members assigned to the project who had active task updates within the last 7 rolling days.</li>
                </ul>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">RAG (Red-Amber-Green) Status:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="rag-dot rag-green d-inline-block me-1"></span> <strong>Green:</strong> Score ≥ 70</li>
                    <li><span class="rag-dot rag-amber d-inline-block me-1"></span> <strong>Amber:</strong> Score 40 – 69</li>
                    <li><span class="rag-dot rag-red d-inline-block me-1"></span> <strong>Red:</strong> Score &lt; 40</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

