                    <li><span class="badge bg-secondary">Idle</span>: exactly <strong>0 committed hours</strong>. This employee has no assigned active work.</li>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-primary">Engaged</span>: Between <strong>1 and 40 committed hours</strong> of active assigned tasks.</li>
                    <li><span class="badge bg-danger">Overloaded</span>: Greater than <strong>40 committed hours</strong> of active assigned tasks.</li>
                </ul>
                <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Velocity Tracking:</h6>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">The system analyzes the <code>TaskHistory</code> table to count how many tasks the user successfully moved to 'Done' status in the current rolling 7 days versus the previous 7 days.</p>
